name: Shiny Satoshi
description: The discovery of the rare "Shiny Satoshi" This artwork was created as part of the #Legato100 project, as a cover art for “Nifty Sax: Genesis #19 – Shiny Satoshi“.  Legato100 is a collaborative project of 100 artworks for 100 music tracks.  The track is available here: https://bit.ly/NiftySax-19  Project’s official page: https://niftysax.com/legato100
